WEBVTT

00:00:59.999 --> 00:00:59.999
Devi Puja,Pune India, 1990-12-03

00:03:24.850 --> 00:03:35.640
Initially, I will Talk in English

00:03:46.077 --> 00:03:53.120
This is not working.

00:03:53.144 --> 00:04:02.520
Initially I will talk in English language
and later on I will talk in Marathi.

00:16:47.817 --> 00:16:54.360
Yesterday, I have told
you in detail

00:16:54.360 --> 00:16:59.640
that we have got so much
treasure of spirituality;

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:02.520
you should have some
appreciation for that.

00:17:02.520 --> 00:17:04.628
When we do not have respect for ourselves,

00:17:04.652 --> 00:17:07.360
how will we be
appreciative of our treasure?

00:17:07.360 --> 00:17:09.938
Every person in India,

00:17:09.962 --> 00:17:12.658
in that also a person from Maharashtra

00:17:12.682 --> 00:17:18.920
should be reckoned as an
image of ardent love for God.

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:21.310
We ourselves don’t have
any idea about ourselves.

00:17:21.310 --> 00:17:23.365
If we are staying in a village

00:17:23.389 --> 00:17:25.358
and are facing lot of troubles,

00:17:25.382 --> 00:17:28.170
then we feel that
we are insignificant beings.

00:17:28.170 --> 00:17:29.770
It is not like that.

00:17:29.783 --> 00:17:32.158
You are going to be of great use;

00:17:32.182 --> 00:17:36.440
only thing is that we should
remember certain things.

00:17:36.440 --> 00:17:38.268
First and foremost thing is that

00:17:38.292 --> 00:17:43.108
we should be completely aware
about religion (“dharma”).

00:17:43.132 --> 00:17:47.005
Every religion that is prevalent in
our country or in any other country,

00:17:47.029 --> 00:17:53.345
in all those countries we can say
that, it is only been mechanized

00:17:53.369 --> 00:17:58.883
or in all it has been made
as a means to earn money.

00:17:58.883 --> 00:18:01.857
This cannot be
religion (“dharma”).

00:18:01.857 --> 00:18:05.825
God does not understand money,
cannot understand bank, nothing.

00:18:05.843 --> 00:18:08.023
If someone asks me to write a
cheque, I do not understand it,

00:18:08.023 --> 00:18:11.280
I ask someone else to
write it and I will sign it.

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:15.748
The people here who plunder your money in
the name of God,

00:18:15.772 --> 00:18:21.080
to give them even a single penny
is wrong, this is the first thing.

00:18:21.080 --> 00:18:24.478
And any person who wears a
saffron robe and comes,

00:18:24.502 --> 00:18:29.188
we start prostrating in front of them.

00:18:29.212 --> 00:18:33.508
The person has come here after being
released from jail

00:18:33.532 --> 00:18:35.747
and is now wearing a saffron robe,

00:18:35.771 --> 00:18:37.503
this thought does not come
to anyone’s mind.

00:18:37.503 --> 00:18:38.943
We directly start.

00:18:38.977 --> 00:18:41.117
The people from villages are simple
(“sadhe”) and straight forward (“saral”) –

00:18:41.117 --> 00:18:45.777
if he says “See, if you give so much money,
then so much good will happen to you”,

00:18:45.777 --> 00:18:49.320
he will start giving money
to such a person.

00:18:49.320 --> 00:18:53.051
Sometime back, I had gone to a village,
everyone started coming

00:18:53.075 --> 00:18:55.548
“we have to take darshan (see)
of Shri Mataji”; one woman came

00:18:55.572 --> 00:18:57.840
and she gave me twenty five paise.

00:18:57.840 --> 00:18:59.240
I told her that I don’t take money;

00:18:59.240 --> 00:19:02.280
She said okay, then I will
give you one rupee, Mataji.

00:19:02.280 --> 00:19:04.388
Means it does not go out of their minds,

00:19:04.412 --> 00:19:05.888
it is fixed in their minds that

00:19:05.912 --> 00:19:08.040
money has to be offered to God.

00:19:08.040 --> 00:19:12.360
But does that God
understand anything money?

00:19:12.360 --> 00:19:15.748
All that is filled in our minds
should be taken out first

00:19:15.772 --> 00:19:18.031
that any person who asks for money,

00:19:18.055 --> 00:19:23.720
such a person is definitely
not close to God.

00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:27.920
This should be explained to
all the villagers by everybody.

00:19:27.920 --> 00:19:30.508
We have many simple (“saadhe”)
innocent (“bhole”) people

00:19:30.520 --> 00:19:34.018
and that is why anywhere
if you just place a stone,

00:19:34.042 --> 00:19:35.365
coat it with vermilion (“sindoor”)

00:19:35.389 --> 00:19:38.200
then someone sits in front of
it to make money.

00:19:38.200 --> 00:19:41.640
Anyone who comes and goes will start prostrating
(“lotangan”) in front of it, offering two paise to him.

00:19:41.640 --> 00:19:45.840
Saints like Nrusinha Saraswati
have done a lot of work on this.

00:19:45.840 --> 00:19:47.711
They have lambasted everyone and
tried their best

00:19:47.735 --> 00:19:50.640
but nobody understands it.

00:19:50.663 --> 00:19:55.548
Saints have, amongst them,
a Brahmin, Nrusinha Saraswati

00:19:55.572 --> 00:19:57.868
used to thrash that person,

00:19:57.892 --> 00:20:00.997
used to throw away the
stone laid out by him.

00:20:00.997 --> 00:20:04.965
Eknath (a saint) was
troubled a lot by people

00:20:04.989 --> 00:20:07.080
because he partook food at Mahaarwada
(a dwelling for low castes India).

00:20:07.080 --> 00:20:09.977
Do monks (“sadhu”) and
saints (“sant”) have any caste?

00:20:09.977 --> 00:20:13.163
Who is a Mahar,
who is a Brahmin?

00:20:13.163 --> 00:20:15.838
And if you see our scriptures (“shastras”),

00:20:15.862 --> 00:20:19.788
if you peep a bit deeper,
you will come to know

00:20:19.812 --> 00:20:24.920
who has written Shri Rama’s character?
That fisherman, Valmiki.

00:20:24.920 --> 00:20:31.680
That fisherman had written the
character of Shri Rama, not any Brahmin.

00:20:31.680 --> 00:20:34.988
So all the madness that is within us

00:20:35.012 --> 00:20:40.427
regarding caste and
creed should be removed.

00:20:40.427 --> 00:20:42.271
There is no meaning to it.

00:20:42.295 --> 00:20:44.960
It is an indication of stupidity.

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:49.960
It is said about the Devi “yaa Devi sarva
bhooteshu, jaati roopena Sansthitha”.

00:20:49.960 --> 00:20:51.880
What does this caste mean?

00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:53.160
What is a caste?

00:20:53.183 --> 00:20:55.828
Caste means something within you

00:20:55.852 --> 00:21:03.010
which you like or your inborn
intelligence is what caste is.

00:21:03.010 --> 00:21:08.040
If any person is in search of
God then that person is a Brahmin.

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:11.101
Das Ganu says

00:21:11.125 --> 00:21:15.268
“Amhasi mhanati Bramhan, Amhi jaanile
nahi Bramha, Amhi Kasale Bramhan?”

00:21:15.292 --> 00:21:18.963
(“I call myself a Brahmin, I have not known the Brahma principle within me, then how can I be a Brahmin?”)

00:21:18.963 --> 00:21:21.640
He himself being a Brahmin, says so.

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:26.360
So all this issue of caste
and creed should be forgotten.

00:21:26.360 --> 00:21:29.530
In Sahaja Yoga we do not
believe in any type of caste or creed.

00:21:29.530 --> 00:21:32.470
We do not believe in
widowhood, first thing.

00:21:32.470 --> 00:21:33.750
Women are widows, and men?

00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:36.880
They are never reckoned as
having lost a wife (widower).

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:41.110
By doing this, we have subjected
women to a lot of atrocity.

00:21:41.110 --> 00:21:44.360
To oppress can never
be righteousness.

00:21:44.360 --> 00:21:47.828
Any kind of atrocity is Iniquity

00:21:47.852 --> 00:21:52.040
and any kind of injustice
is also Iniquity.

00:21:52.040 --> 00:21:54.967
So when you come to Sahaja Yoga,
you need to bear in mind

00:21:54.967 --> 00:22:02.685
that all these atrocious practices,

00:22:02.709 --> 00:22:08.342
due to which Hell has been
created in our country,

00:22:08.342 --> 00:22:11.709
we don’t believe them and
will never believe in such things.

00:22:11.709 --> 00:22:17.280
In the case of caste, we
have a very horrible situation.

00:22:17.280 --> 00:22:19.938
And to speak of marriages

00:22:19.962 --> 00:22:22.160
now we don’t
have any missions to accomplish,

00:22:22.160 --> 00:22:24.240
we don’t have to climb Simhagadh (name of a fort
in Maharashtra which means the “Lion’s fort”),

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:26.520
we do not have to conquer
any fort, nothing like that.

00:22:26.520 --> 00:22:29.240
So what else can one do sitting idly – just
arrange our sons and daughters marriages.

00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:31.173
That’s it.
There is nothing else to do.

00:22:31.173 --> 00:22:34.920
It is very surprising.

00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:44.370
I realized that they put me in 96 Kuli
Maratha community when I was born.

00:22:44.370 --> 00:22:46.770
I asked, why did you put me in
that 96 Kuli Maratha community?

00:22:46.770 --> 00:22:49.628
In that clan, all are drunkards

00:22:49.652 --> 00:22:52.600
and they torture their
women so much;

00:22:52.600 --> 00:22:53.945
and in case of marriages,

00:22:53.969 --> 00:22:57.308
it can happen only within the same
clan, the 96 Kuli Maratha community;

00:22:57.332 --> 00:23:00.760
all are useless people.

00:23:00.760 --> 00:23:04.880
If any girl is given to a
well-educated boy then finished.

00:23:04.880 --> 00:23:10.320
Searching takes so much effort – but
they subject the girl to so much torture.

00:23:10.320 --> 00:23:12.000
What is this behaviour?

00:23:12.050 --> 00:23:15.800
Are this 96 kuli created by God?

00:23:15.800 --> 00:23:18.108
Everyone’s nose, face looks the same,

00:23:18.132 --> 00:23:21.200
everyone’s issues are similar

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:23.908
when the way of laughing
and talking is similar,

00:23:23.932 --> 00:23:26.000
when they are children of the same mother,

00:23:26.000 --> 00:23:29.005
how can it be said that this
person cannot marry that person,

00:23:29.029 --> 00:23:30.410
that person cannot marry this person.

00:23:30.410 --> 00:23:32.211
Then take dowry, take this and take that

00:23:32.235 --> 00:23:39.120
Sahaja Yoga has come to cleanse all
these dirty things in our caste/community.

00:23:39.120 --> 00:23:40.250
To make everything
clean and tidy.

00:23:40.250 --> 00:23:42.320
See how much trouble
it is to do all this.

00:23:42.343 --> 00:23:45.543
Today you have a daughter
so you face these issues.

00:23:45.597 --> 00:23:51.240
Tomorrow if you have a son,
you will trouble others similarly.

00:23:51.240 --> 00:23:57.308
Although, Sahaja Yoga belongs to
sages (“sadhu”) and saints (“sant”),

00:23:57.332 --> 00:23:59.400
it does not belong to
Ascetics (“sanyastha”).

00:23:59.400 --> 00:24:00.665
Being in the society,

00:24:00.689 --> 00:24:02.325
helping society to progress,

00:24:02.349 --> 00:24:06.548
helping in refining the thoughts
of the people in the society

00:24:06.572 --> 00:24:11.630
Sahaja Yoga is such a catalyst.

00:24:11.630 --> 00:24:15.548
In your life, those who call themselves
as Sahaja Yogis,

00:24:15.572 --> 00:24:17.868
if they are also having a narrow vision,

00:24:17.892 --> 00:24:20.603
then they need to realize that they
have not yet understood Sahaja Yoga.

00:24:20.603 --> 00:24:22.085
This is a work of the universe,

00:24:22.109 --> 00:24:24.720
we have set out to unite the world,

00:24:24.720 --> 00:24:27.598
instead of that – we belong to this city,
you belong to that city,

00:24:27.622 --> 00:24:29.131
this and that

00:24:29.155 --> 00:24:30.760
Has this given any benefit?

00:24:30.760 --> 00:24:34.000
Has anybody
benefitted from this?

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:38.603
What is the benefit from this,
first you should first observe this.

00:24:38.603 --> 00:24:43.120
Has anyone benefitted by
marrying in the same community?

00:24:43.120 --> 00:24:46.600
The other day, one woman
came to fight with me on this issue.

00:24:46.600 --> 00:24:51.108
I showed her 10 of her relatives, said
now see these people,

00:24:51.132 --> 00:24:54.840
your relations by marriage.

00:24:54.840 --> 00:24:57.751
But Dnyaneshwar has mentioned in
Pasaydaan that

00:24:57.775 --> 00:25:00.520
“Techi Soyarika hoti te”

00:25:00.520 --> 00:25:03.480
which means “these
are your relations”.

00:25:03.480 --> 00:25:07.880
What was mentioned in Pasaydan
that indicates Sahaja Yoga?

00:25:07.880 --> 00:25:10.508
Sages, saints have not accepted this;

00:25:10.532 --> 00:25:13.520
how much they were tortured because
they were the children of ascetics .

00:25:13.520 --> 00:25:15.200
Ascetics had children.

00:25:15.247 --> 00:25:18.560
Did anyone’s father
tell them to do this?

00:25:18.587 --> 00:25:20.087
How much they have been tortured,

00:25:20.087 --> 00:25:21.267
how much Tukaram was tortured,

00:25:21.267 --> 00:25:23.778
how much was Eknath tortured

00:25:23.802 --> 00:25:27.760
as he ate food at a low
caste person’s place.

00:25:27.760 --> 00:25:31.628
It is like this. While staying
on the land of sages and saints,

00:25:31.652 --> 00:25:36.720
we should behave like them.

00:25:36.720 --> 00:25:38.760
Look at their preaching’s (“abhanga”),

00:25:38.760 --> 00:25:40.348
what  have they told –

00:25:40.372 --> 00:25:42.520
what has Tukaram said to Vitthala

00:25:42.544 --> 00:25:46.840
“Tu mahar jhalas he bara jhala”  “It is
good that you became a lower caste person”.

00:25:46.840 --> 00:25:50.960
Vitthala didn’t
assault him for that.

00:25:50.960 --> 00:25:54.883
“Zala Mahar Pandharinath” – “Pandarinath
(Vitthala) has become a lower caste person.”

00:25:54.883 --> 00:25:59.217
He has said such a profound
thing, but does it get into anyone’s head?

00:25:59.217 --> 00:26:04.920
If Pandharinath can become a
lower caste person, then who are you?

00:26:04.920 --> 00:26:09.298
Just chanting the devotional songs of sages
and saints and banging the discs

00:26:09.322 --> 00:26:13.200
but the essence of it
should percolate.

00:26:13.200 --> 00:26:21.837
All of them worked on the
superstition blind faith and herd mentality.

00:26:21.837 --> 00:26:25.988
Dnyaneshwar told about the path
further and then said (out of frustration),

00:26:26.012 --> 00:26:29.583
I don’t want to do this and then
took his entrancement (“Samadhi”).

00:26:29.583 --> 00:26:33.277
These idiots won’t listen,
sometime later when they realize,

00:26:33.277 --> 00:26:34.477
they may read these very books.

00:26:34.477 --> 00:26:39.800
Now all these foreigners
read their books.

00:26:39.800 --> 00:26:43.600
Now their tour of
Maharashtra is over.

00:26:43.600 --> 00:26:47.040
They perceive you people
sitting next to God as for them

00:26:47.040 --> 00:26:51.640
Maharashtra is a great place.

00:26:51.640 --> 00:26:54.880
They really consider Maharashtra as a
Great country (“Maha- rashtra”)

00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:58.880
and they consider people
of Maharashtra as God.

00:26:58.880 --> 00:27:01.240
Because such great traditions you have,

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:03.523
you are sitting in the land of saints.

00:27:03.523 --> 00:27:04.310
you have taken birth here.

00:27:04.310 --> 00:27:08.640
Means how great you
must be is what they think.

00:27:08.640 --> 00:27:12.317
But old habits die hard.

00:27:12.317 --> 00:27:13.997
Again, the same things.

00:27:14.010 --> 00:27:17.600
Now yesterday, everyone had
catch on their Vishuddhi chakra.

00:27:17.600 --> 00:27:22.440
This chakra. Why?
I know, tobacco.

00:27:22.440 --> 00:27:25.148
In Maharashtra, one cannot
do without tobacco,

00:27:25.172 --> 00:27:27.077
even if it causes cancer or death.

00:27:27.077 --> 00:27:32.360
From where this evil has come in
Maharashtra, I don’t understand.

00:27:32.360 --> 00:27:39.748
The poor sages and saints,

00:27:39.772 --> 00:27:43.600
all of them advised
not to consume intoxicating substances.

00:27:43.600 --> 00:27:48.297
Sai Nath had burnt all the
tobacco and smoked it up,

00:27:48.297 --> 00:27:53.640
like Shiva (Shankara), but still
everyone is stuck to tobacco.

00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:55.225
Wherever they go they consume tobacco,

00:27:55.249 --> 00:27:57.897
even while going to Vitthala they consume
tobacco before leaving.

00:27:57.897 --> 00:28:01.600
Vithala does not
like tobacco at all.

00:28:01.643 --> 00:28:03.840
Vitthala sits on the Vishuddhi Chakra

00:28:03.840 --> 00:28:09.800
and still why do you consume
tobacco and go to (worship) him?

00:28:09.800 --> 00:28:12.920
You should know the purpose,

00:28:12.920 --> 00:28:14.510
you should hold to the gist of it.

00:28:14.510 --> 00:28:16.777
Then you say for the sake of it ,
Mataji we believe in God so much.

00:28:16.777 --> 00:28:20.760
Some ladies were telling me,
Lady – We worship the Devi so much.

00:28:20.760 --> 00:28:26.520
Mataji – What else?
Lady – Well, my husband
drinks alchohol a bit. Mataji – Is it?

00:28:26.520 --> 00:28:29.520
And then becomes disgraced.

00:28:29.520 --> 00:28:31.510
And your (husband)?

00:28:31.510 --> 00:28:34.810
Lady – He likes to play cards.

00:28:34.810 --> 00:28:36.360
Mataji -Is that so?

00:28:36.360 --> 00:28:42.880
So after playing cards, he goes
to perform aarati, Devi’s aarati.

00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:48.640
This impurity has increased
very much in our society,

00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:53.640
this is not acceptable to the Goddess,

00:28:53.640 --> 00:28:58.030
all such things are not
acceptable to the Goddess at all.

00:28:58.030 --> 00:28:59.710
Then you get whipped.

00:28:59.777 --> 00:29:02.560
Then when you get whipped, you
will ask why did this happen to us?

00:29:02.560 --> 00:29:03.835
I am such a great devotee of God,

00:29:03.859 --> 00:29:05.148
I am such a great devotee of Shiva,

00:29:05.172 --> 00:29:06.871
I am such a great devotee of Dattatreya,

00:29:06.895 --> 00:29:08.920
then how did this happen to me?

00:29:08.920 --> 00:29:11.880
Hence, first get connected with HIM.

00:29:11.880 --> 00:29:16.365
Devotees of Dattatreya should definitely
be having a trouble of the stomach,

00:29:16.389 --> 00:29:18.331
take it in writing,

00:29:18.355 --> 00:29:20.920
I am not lying.

00:29:20.920 --> 00:29:22.811
Anyone who is having a stomach problem,

00:29:22.835 --> 00:29:26.168
ask them ‘are you a
devotee of Dattatreya’. ‘Yes.’

00:29:26.200 --> 00:29:32.080
They should have the trouble of the
stomach because Dattatreya, is the deity

00:29:32.080 --> 00:29:35.335
residing around this area of the stomach which is the
place of our righteousness (“dharma”) , called the Void,

00:29:35.359 --> 00:29:39.800
we don’t have a photo
here so you can’t see it.

00:29:39.800 --> 00:29:44.280
People keep on chanting Datta Datta
in vain without getting connected to HIM.

00:29:44.280 --> 00:29:48.560
In real sense, Datta is
actually Mohammed Sahib.

00:29:48.560 --> 00:29:52.680
So the Muslims will also
have the trouble of stomach.

00:29:52.680 --> 00:29:57.160
Simply chanting Mohammed – Mohammed,
Muslims will not achieve anything.

00:29:57.223 --> 00:30:01.043
Need to have connection.

00:30:01.043 --> 00:30:04.663
Even they do not understand
sometimes, that we believe in God

00:30:04.663 --> 00:30:06.930
and then how is this coming on us?

00:30:06.977 --> 00:30:09.360
Why are we in such trouble?

00:30:09.360 --> 00:30:13.720
The reason for that is that
you have still not understood.

00:30:13.720 --> 00:30:17.468
Mohammed Sahib has told this specifically

00:30:17.492 --> 00:30:22.068
that such a time will come which he has
called as “Qiyama”, means resurrection,

00:30:22.092 --> 00:30:25.737
resurrection will take place; at that
time your hands will speak.

00:30:25.737 --> 00:30:28.470
His preachings are
about Sahaja Yoga only.

00:30:28.497 --> 00:30:31.143
One such person will
come who will tell everything.

00:30:31.143 --> 00:30:33.717
Everything has been told.

00:30:33.717 --> 00:30:36.868
Muslims are not some other people,

00:30:36.892 --> 00:30:38.668
Hindus are not some other people ,

00:30:38.692 --> 00:30:41.000
everyone belongs to us.

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:43.188
But when you have not found the path,

00:30:43.212 --> 00:30:46.360
you see it this way only.
It is the same for the blind.

00:30:46.360 --> 00:30:49.428
Like blind people cannot see green and red,

00:30:49.452 --> 00:30:53.948
similarly they cannot
see that we all are one.

00:30:53.972 --> 00:30:58.240
That is why these quarrels,
these skirmishes and what not.

00:30:58.240 --> 00:31:00.240
Does this have any meaning?

00:31:00.240 --> 00:31:04.840
Quarrelsome nature is very
common place in Maharashtra.

00:31:04.840 --> 00:31:07.400
The other thing is family feuds.

00:31:07.400 --> 00:31:11.203
If anyone advances even slightly,
then (others) start poisoning my ears.

00:31:11.203 --> 00:31:15.600
I have decided to close
my ears now, I say.

00:31:15.600 --> 00:31:19.680
No one knows this that
I understand everything.

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:22.488
They will come and tell me
that this person is like this,

00:31:22.512 --> 00:31:24.603
a terrible politician, Mataji,
please be careful of this person.

00:31:24.603 --> 00:31:27.200
I said that I know more
about him than you.

00:31:27.200 --> 00:31:29.320
I will tell you
everything later on.

00:31:29.320 --> 00:31:31.017
They will then look at
me with great dismay.

00:31:31.017 --> 00:31:32.170
How did you know?

00:31:32.170 --> 00:31:35.920
I can understand, don’t
tell me about useless things.

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:39.600
This person’s (views) on that person, that person’s
(views) on this person, just no end to this.

00:31:39.600 --> 00:31:40.877
Then how will Sahaja
Yoga proliferate?

00:31:40.877 --> 00:31:43.400
These people don’t
have these things.

00:31:43.400 --> 00:31:44.697
Not at all.

00:31:44.697 --> 00:31:48.125
Once these people come to Sahaja yoga,
they become so humble,

00:31:48.149 --> 00:31:49.457
they are so humble

00:31:49.457 --> 00:31:50.910
that they have
achieved a great thing.

00:31:50.910 --> 00:31:53.840
We do not have
any idea about this.

00:31:53.840 --> 00:31:57.598
No quarrels, no skirmishes, no badmouthing
each other

00:31:57.622 --> 00:32:00.640
because I do not like it.

00:32:00.640 --> 00:32:05.960
Speak up right up front,
not behind the back.

00:32:05.960 --> 00:32:12.680
These people, who do
not have the foundation,

00:32:12.680 --> 00:32:15.908
do not have the
perspectives of the saints,

00:32:15.932 --> 00:32:19.605
who did not have kings
like Shri Ram ,

00:32:19.629 --> 00:32:22.588
did not have warriors like Shivaji ,

00:32:22.612 --> 00:32:27.903
those people have advanced so
much, and where are we languishing?

00:32:27.903 --> 00:32:32.480
They have achieved so
much then why shouldn’t we?

00:32:32.480 --> 00:32:34.843
How great our past
heritage (“poorva pithika”),

00:32:34.843 --> 00:32:43.160
we are people who have sat on
thrones and how are we behaving?

00:32:43.160 --> 00:32:49.800
People get obligated
to useless people

00:32:49.800 --> 00:32:55.868
and being obligated,
they lose their virtuosity.

00:32:55.892 --> 00:32:59.720
In this Maharashtra we have to do
a lot of awakening

00:32:59.720 --> 00:33:04.763
and it will happen because
Maharashtra has this heritage (“sampada”)

00:33:04.763 --> 00:33:06.683
that is not present anywhere
else in this world.

00:33:06.683 --> 00:33:08.270
That is why I am putting
in so much effort over here.

00:33:08.270 --> 00:33:10.151
That is why I have
taken birth in Maharashtra

00:33:10.175 --> 00:33:17.760
and have been putting efforts in
Maharashtra since so many years.

00:33:17.760 --> 00:33:22.440
So people should realize
what their responsibility is,

00:33:22.440 --> 00:33:24.333
what Maharashtra’s
responsibility is?

00:33:24.333 --> 00:33:25.868
Even if you are staying in a village,

00:33:25.892 --> 00:33:30.217
are uneducated, still your
internal state is very superior.

00:33:30.217 --> 00:33:34.068
So you need to achieve that state

00:33:34.092 --> 00:33:36.280
and show the whole world

00:33:36.280 --> 00:33:39.748
that an ordinary farmer from
Maharashtra

00:33:39.772 --> 00:33:42.720
is also of a very high caliber.

00:33:42.720 --> 00:33:45.240
It is easy to parrot things out,

00:33:45.240 --> 00:33:48.800
will keep on reading Mahtmya
like a learned ass.

00:33:48.800 --> 00:33:51.160
What are you going
to achieve by reading.

00:33:51.160 --> 00:33:53.748
Revision after revision,

00:33:53.772 --> 00:33:57.200
one weekly discourse after another.

00:33:57.200 --> 00:33:59.333
Has anybody
gained by doing that?

00:33:59.377 --> 00:34:02.511
Whichever village you go, ‘Mataji, there
is a weekly discourse going on.’

00:34:02.535 --> 00:34:07.680
What will happen due to
that discourse of yours?

00:34:07.680 --> 00:34:10.600
Is it going to do any good?

00:34:10.600 --> 00:34:12.671
So you need to get your awakening

00:34:12.695 --> 00:34:16.040
and being awakened, you need to
understand why you are having this plight?

00:34:16.040 --> 00:34:18.440
Why did we get
into all this trouble?

00:34:18.477 --> 00:34:21.317
And to get your awakening is not difficult; it
is a possession (“sampada”) inbuilt within you.

00:34:21.317 --> 00:34:23.280
The complete
power is within you.

00:34:23.280 --> 00:34:24.543
What is yours needs
to be given to you.

00:34:24.543 --> 00:34:27.600
‘What is yours is with you’
and it needs to be given to you.

00:34:27.600 --> 00:34:29.761
There is nothing here for me to give
and take;

00:34:29.785 --> 00:34:30.830
there is no favor from me.

00:34:30.830 --> 00:34:32.317
Does Mother do any favors?

00:34:32.317 --> 00:34:33.883
You believe if you have to.

00:34:33.883 --> 00:34:37.617
But Mother does everything
for her own happiness.

00:34:37.617 --> 00:34:41.588
Now the specialty of this
city is , of this place is that,

00:34:41.612 --> 00:34:47.588
the land we have taken at Shera
is only after seeing the vibrations

00:34:47.612 --> 00:34:50.120
and then we took this land.

00:34:50.120 --> 00:34:51.681
Now (people) are going to
come and stay here,

00:34:51.705 --> 00:34:57.560
so on behalf of you all I have

00:34:57.560 --> 00:35:00.480
informed them that we
have purchased the place.

00:35:00.480 --> 00:35:04.828
These are all devotees
of the Goddess,

00:35:04.852 --> 00:35:06.563
so they need to be looked after.

00:35:06.563 --> 00:35:08.878
There is a designated location
of the Goddess here

00:35:08.902 --> 00:35:11.188
and in front of them;

00:35:11.212 --> 00:35:15.920
we should
show how deep you all are.

00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:18.123
You can prosper in all aspects.

00:35:18.123 --> 00:35:20.863
Only thing is that you
first need to achieve depth.

00:35:20.863 --> 00:35:24.263
Otherwise after you progress,
you will again start drinking

00:35:24.263 --> 00:35:26.337
or will do some filthy thing.

00:35:26.337 --> 00:35:28.011
The first thing you need is that

00:35:28.035 --> 00:35:31.560
your inner power should be awakened.

00:35:31.560 --> 00:35:35.400
You should have this desire in you
that we need to get our awakening.

00:35:35.400 --> 00:35:38.291
Today you have come
for the Pooja,

00:35:38.315 --> 00:35:41.920
in the Pooja, energy flows.

00:35:41.920 --> 00:35:46.600
Usually we don’t allow people
who are not Sahaja Yogis.

00:35:46.600 --> 00:35:49.978
Those who have not got their awakening,

00:35:50.002 --> 00:35:51.160
we do not allow them to come for the Pooja,

00:35:51.160 --> 00:35:53.950
because he cannot do it,
he cannot understand it.

00:35:53.950 --> 00:35:56.158
But if you are sitting in humility,

00:35:56.182 --> 00:35:58.440
everyone will benefit from the Pooja and

00:35:58.440 --> 00:36:00.030
everyone will feel satisfied.

00:36:00.030 --> 00:36:01.630
So you have to sit in humility.

00:36:01.630 --> 00:36:04.640
We should keep in mind that
we need to achieve something.

00:36:04.640 --> 00:36:08.577
This is going to happen through
the virtuosity accumulated in you.

00:36:08.577 --> 00:36:10.870
After that you come and tell me.

00:36:10.870 --> 00:36:16.720
Then I will get this letter, that ‘Mataji,
we are swimming in the ocean of joy.’

00:36:16.720 --> 00:36:21.563
To give this, I am moving
around villages.

00:36:21.563 --> 00:36:24.117
Since last 20 years
this effort is going on.

00:36:24.142 --> 00:36:27.470
Now let’s see how much
work gets done in Maharashtra.

00:36:27.489 --> 00:36:32.777
In that way, in Delhi, beyond Delhi in the
towns and villages, a lot of work is being done.

00:36:32.777 --> 00:36:36.269
Same way it should happen here
because this is the land of saints

00:36:36.293 --> 00:36:39.739
and this is your inheritance.

00:36:39.739 --> 00:36:42.960
You need to satisfy the saints.

00:36:42.960 --> 00:36:45.388
The saints should feel that these people

00:36:45.412 --> 00:36:46.430
have got what we have given them.

00:36:46.430 --> 00:36:48.771
It should not be a mere meaningless blabber

00:36:48.795 --> 00:36:50.960
and also not just banging
the crymbals (discs).

00:36:50.960 --> 00:36:53.148
The reverberations of the crymbals

00:36:53.172 --> 00:36:56.560
that should emerge from you

00:36:56.560 --> 00:36:59.530
and the arrangement for that is very easy.

00:36:59.530 --> 00:37:02.618
The people who are sitting in
the sun can come and sit here,

00:37:02.642 --> 00:37:04.203
there is space here in the
front, come and sit here.

00:37:04.203 --> 00:37:05.877
There is time for Pooja,
come and sit here.

00:37:05.877 --> 00:37:10.037
You can come here and sit, there
is space here, come in the front.

00:37:10.063 --> 00:37:13.135
You can sit there,
after all you are at a height.

00:37:13.163 --> 00:37:14.470
Come and sit at the front.

00:37:14.470 --> 00:37:18.640
Come, like this
sit in the front.

00:37:18.640 --> 00:37:26.920
Sit in the shade, it will
take a long time for this.

00:37:26.920 --> 00:37:33.295
Don’t sit in the sun,
congregation (“mandali”)

00:37:33.319 --> 00:37:41.480
don’t sit in the sun, don’t sit
in the sun. Sit in the shade.

00:37:41.480 --> 00:37:45.280
It is a nice breeze blowing.

00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:48.640
Alright.

00:37:51.813 --> 00:38:02.200
Now who is coming for the Pooja?

00:38:02.200 --> 00:38:06.200
Shri Mataji responding to a
question by Sahaja Yogi: Hmmm.

00:38:06.200 --> 00:38:07.447
A Sahaja Yogi is asking a question
to Shri Mataji: Washing your feet.

00:38:07.447 --> 00:38:09.740
Shri Mataji responding to a question by
Sahaja Yogi: Yaaa (Yes). Shri Ganeshas.

00:38:09.740 --> 00:38:18.280
There are how, many
children here I think.

00:38:18.280 --> 00:38:23.640
There will be many children here.

00:38:23.640 --> 00:38:25.320
Can you check and come?

00:38:25.363 --> 00:38:31.360
Small children between 5 to 10 years,
come and sit here.

00:38:31.360 --> 00:38:38.400
4 to 10 years.

00:38:38.400 --> 00:38:44.613
A Sahaja Yogi talking in the
background: Children 5 to 10 years old.

00:38:44.613 --> 00:38:47.843
Shri Mataji: 4 to 10.

00:38:47.843 --> 00:38:52.003
A Sahaja Yogi talking in the
background: 4 to 10 all the children.

00:38:52.057 --> 00:38:54.590
Sit down.

99:59:59.999 --> 99:59:59.999
Devi Puja,Pune India, 19901203
